    <item>
      <title>Raw Material To Create Space And Time</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/wiaposts/raw-material-to-create-space-and-time/</link>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2018 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <author>hari@dasarpai.com (Dr. Hari Thapliyaal)</author>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/wiaposts/raw-material-to-create-space-and-time/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;
    &lt;figure&gt;
      &lt;img class=&#34;my-0 rounded-md&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; src=&#34;../../assets/images/wiapost/5065-Raw-Material-To-Create-Space-And-Time.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;Raw Material To Create Space And Time&#34; /&gt;
      
    &lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;h1 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Raw Material To Create Space And Time 
    &lt;div id=&#34;raw-material-to-create-space-and-time&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
    
    &lt;span
        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100&#34;&gt;
        &lt;a class=&#34;group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700&#34;
            style=&#34;text-decoration-line: none !important;&#34; href=&#34;#raw-material-to-create-space-and-time&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
    &lt;/span&gt;        
    
&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Time (Kaala) is 100% mind’s creation.  &lt;br&gt;
There is no physical time.  &lt;br&gt;
Akasha is the “voidness” of objects.  &lt;br&gt;
But, what Object? Atom or Mango or Table or planet?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;All objects are in the space and have space inside.  &lt;br&gt;
So sensory perception of human is different  &lt;br&gt;
and it is different for microbiological being.  &lt;br&gt;
For us, microparticles don’t exist in normal sensory experience  &lt;br&gt;
so there is void and hence Akasha  &lt;br&gt;
That is why we wave our hand in the air  &lt;br&gt;
and say there is nothing.  &lt;br&gt;
But for the microbe, it is not Akasha.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
